{"id": "art-1382", "label": "Art. 1382", "title": "Art. 1382", "slug": "art-1382", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_563694305\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2241\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_563694305\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 138<sup>2</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_757861820\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2240\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_757861820\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Prin actul constitutiv sau prin hot&#259;râre a\nadun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> se poate\nprevedea c&#259; unul sau mai <span class=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span> membri ai\nconsiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> trebuie s&#259; fie\n<span class=SpellE>independen&#355;i</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_492640865\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2239\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_492640865\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>La desemnarea\nadministratorului independent, adunarea general&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\nva avea în vedere urm&#259;toarele criterii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_518369299\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2238\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_518369299\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)s&#259; nu fie director al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nsau al unei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> controlate de\nc&#259;tre aceasta <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> s&#259; nu fi îndeplinit o\nastfel de <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ie</span> în ultimii 5 ani;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_841209358\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2237\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_841209358\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)s&#259; nu fi fost salariat al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nsau al unei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> controlate de\nc&#259;tre aceasta ori s&#259; fi avut un astfel de raport de munc&#259; în\nultimii 5 ani;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_592177541\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2236\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_592177541\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)s&#259; nu primeasc&#259; sau s&#259; fi primit de la\nsocietate ori de la o societate controlat&#259; de aceasta o <span\nclass=SpellE>remunera&#355;ie</span> suplimentar&#259; sau alte avantaje,\naltele decât cele corespunzând <span class=SpellE>calit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nsale de administrator neexecutiv;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2027414883\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2235\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2027414883\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)s&#259; nu fie <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span>\nsemnificativ al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1857336695\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2234\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1857336695\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)s&#259; nu aib&#259; sau s&#259; fi avut în ultimul an <span\nclass=SpellE>rela&#355;ii</span> de afaceri cu societatea ori cu o societate\ncontrolat&#259; de aceasta, fie personal, fie ca asociat, <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span>,\nadministrator, director sau salariat al unei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\ncare are astfel de <span class=SpellE>rela&#355;ii</span> cu societatea,\ndac&#259;, prin caracterul lor <span class=SpellE>substan&#355;ial</span>,\nacestea sunt de natur&#259; a-i afecta obiectivitatea;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1676580425\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2233\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1676580425\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)s&#259; nu fie sau s&#259; fi fost în ultimii 3 ani\nauditor financiar ori asociat salariat al actualului auditor financiar al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> sau al unei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\ncontrolate de aceasta;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1864168234\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2232\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1864168234\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)s&#259; fie director într-o alt&#259; societate în care\nun director al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> este\nadministrator neexecutiv;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1500998403\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2231\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1500998403\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)s&#259; nu fi fost administrator neexecutiv al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> mai mult de 3 mandate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_865071097\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2230\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_865071097\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)s&#259; nu aib&#259; <span class=SpellE>rela&#355;ii</span>\nde familie cu o persoan&#259; aflat&#259; în una dintre <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute la lit. a) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> d).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}